11:09.836 --> 11:11.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT LICHTER: Yes, Donald
Trump should go
back a couple of hundred years
and see the

11:11.037 --> 11:13.339 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
