toward the end
of '08 and when she was kind of
flirting with

12:26.379 --> 12:28.147 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
her own presidential run.

12:28.181 --> 12:31.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And other colleagues I have
talked to who
are much older than I am refer
me back the

12:31.818 --> 12:34.621 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
