to be in,
as a country right now, where
this is a conversation

12:41.661 --> 12:43.429 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
we're having.

12:43.463 --> 12:45.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Jim Rutenberg,
staying with
you, I want to come back to
something you

12:45.398 --> 12:51.804 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
