columns, a
senior editor at the Web site
American Conservative,

12:51.838 --> 12:54.941 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and he -- it's Rod Dreher, I
think is how
you say his name.

12:54.974 --> 13:00.680 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He said: "Mainstream journalists
are interested
in every kind of diversity,
except the kind

13:00.713 --> 13:03.383 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
