and poor white
people."

13:11.958 --> 13:13.860 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's pretty sweeping, isn't
it?

13:13.893 --> 13:18.698 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JIM RUTENBERG: It's a sweeping
generalization,
but, that said, I think, look,
we're not perfect.

13:18.731 --> 13:22.535 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And for what most of our
conversations so
far have been a defense of the
press, but

13:22.568 --> 13:24.404 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the press -- let's face it.

13:24.437 --> 13:27.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A big part of the country is
primed to believe
what Donald Trump is telling
them about the

13:27.440 --> 13:28.641 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
press.

13:28.675 --> 13:30.176 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And the press needs to
definitely take a look
at itself.

13:30.209 --> 13:32.011 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And look, there is something to
it.

13:32.045 --> 13:36.082 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There is a cultural mind-set
that I think
even goes across the kind of
ideological divide

13:36.115 --> 13:37.850 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
