13:48.461 --> 13:54.534 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: At the same time,
we know that
-- you have talked, Robert
Lichter, about

13:54.567 --> 14:01.040 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
