supporting Donald Trump.

14:04.243 --> 14:09.882 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT LICHTER: Yes, I think Jim
Rutenberg
was quite right that
journalists, national

14:09.916 --> 14:13.486 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
