pitchforks.

14:33.906 --> 14:39.946 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think there is a kind of bias
in that portrayal
of his supporters.

14:39.979 --> 14:43.950 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There are some of those people,
but he obviously
wouldn't be running in the
40-odd percent

14:43.983 --> 14:47.053 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
