-- with everybody
like that.

14:47.086 --> 14:49.455 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: No question about
that.

14:49.489 --> 14:50.656 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Robert Lichter, we thank you.

14:50.690 --> 14:53.025 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
