two lines.

26:26.518 --> 26:30.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
First is, on the distrust in
government, on
the feeling that the economy is
rigged, that

26:30.422 --> 26:34.059 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
