surrogates say
all the time the economy is
rigged, the election

26:38.230 --> 26:39.832 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
is rigged.

26:39.865 --> 26:44.803 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And this is sort of the fallout
from that.

26:44.837 --> 26:48.006 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But also we're seeing a shift
now from what
happened in the primaries, where
you had people

26:48.040 --> 26:52.644 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
