top 1 percent.

27:06.024 --> 27:09.661 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The rest of it, the other 99
percent, just
don't get the gains.

27:09.695 --> 27:13.899 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we're seeing that now play
out both on
the campaign trail and also in
this survey.

27:13.932 --> 27:17.536 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right, Kai
Ryssdal of
Marketplace and our partners at
"Frontline"

27:17.569 --> 27:21.440 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on How the Deck Is Stacked,
joining us from
L.A. today, thanks so much.

27:21.473 --> 27:27.880 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
KAI RYSSDAL: You bet.

27:27.913 --> 27:31.950 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
