tough rhetoric,
makes this a different year for
teachers and

43:29.407 --> 43:30.608 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
students.

43:30.641 --> 43:32.944 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's the focus of this week's
Making the
Grade segment.

43:32.977 --> 43:37.448 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
