to this?

43:46.757 --> 43:50.995 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Andrew Orzel
is getting
his seniors ready for tomorrow
night's debate.

43:51.028 --> 43:55.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And given what was discussed
right off the
bat in the last debate, some of
the students

43:55.533 --> 43:59.036 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
