what the candidates
might want to focus on.

43:59.070 --> 44:01.739 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ADDISON GUYNN, Student: I almost
stopped watching
the last one.

44:01.772 --> 44:08.145 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It was getting so combative, so
loud, it was
kind of just hard to get a --
like, at one

44:08.179 --> 44:10.381 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
