to handle mentally.

44:10.414 --> 44:13.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANDREW ORZEL: And I, as a
teacher, honestly
have been frustrated by this, in
that normally,

44:13.985 --> 44:17.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
