44:25.029 --> 44:29.834 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Even, so Orzel
is assigning
his students to watch again.

44:29.867 --> 44:34.839 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He asked whether the debates
might change
anyone's mind and their
expectations if the

44:34.872 --> 44:36.641 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
