going to expect
more in debates in the future.

45:02.500 --> 45:07.538 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's potentially damaging to
democracy
as an institution in America for
many years

45:07.572 --> 45:09.006 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
