45:56.354 --> 46:01.325 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD HOUSE, Teacher, Gunston
Middle School:
I think a lot of them, words
they used, entertained.

46:01.359 --> 46:06.330 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
