classroom.

46:08.666 --> 46:11.402 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when we're talking about the
debate, when
we're discussing it, we're going
to focus

46:11.435 --> 46:13.337 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
