46:13.371 --> 46:16.741 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, for example, for the first
debate, I had
them pick two or three issues
that were focused

46:16.774 --> 46:18.009 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
on the debate.

46:18.042 --> 46:19.477 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What did each candidate say
about them?

46:19.510 --> 46:21.479 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And then we can have a classroom
discussion.

46:21.512 --> 46:25.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I do not want to take time to
really focus
on some of the personal behavior
that the

46:25.883 --> 46:29.086 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
