and the expectations
that I have when they walk into
my classroom.

46:33.224 --> 46:37.461 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And this election should be
about policy and
it should be about the issues
and focusing

46:37.495 --> 46:39.130 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on them.

46:39.163 --> 46:40.931 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Chris, your
high school
students, what did they think so
far?

46:40.965 --> 46:43.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRISTOPHER CAVANAUGH, Teacher,
Plainfield
High School: I think they have
been a little

46:43.501 --> 46:47.104 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
