the rhetoric
that's been used in the debates.

47:04.889 --> 47:09.427 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, it's been a tough row to
hoe, so to speak.

47:09.460 --> 47:13.264 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Chris, staying
with you
for a second, how do you
navigate some of

47:13.297 --> 47:19.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
