52:22.206 --> 52:29.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Tonight on
"Frontline": a joint
investigation with ProPublica
into efforts

52:29.446 --> 52:32.282 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
